x_nuvo_diag_probes.description:
CAD Record Details process is stuck at Space Creation - Processing status. Unable to proceed further.
-> geoCache Attachment not created -> geoCache records are not created with active entries
Check for CAD Record Datails with space creation - processing status for X amount of time (30 minutes) and check for the absence of attachment and geoCache records.
The possible issues are due to the following:
1.) Autocad user and password system property should be present and defined. (check to ensure user exist, have the right roles (rest_api, x_nuvo_eam_space_admin), password matches by checking updated timestamp, user is active and not locked out) 2.) check to make sure the endpoint is reachable with the user (rewrite it to be diagnostic do not run the actual logic)
x_nuvo_diag_probes.name: CAD import stuck at space creation
x_nuvo_diag_probes.remediation: Click Build GeoCache UI Action related link from floor record on x_nuvo_eam_space table
x_nuvo_diag_probes.sys_name: CAD import stuck at space creation
